	"nodes":[
		{"id":"orb_title","type":"text","text":"# ORB + ENTROPY STRATEGY DASHBOARD","x":0,"y":0,"width":2820,"height":70,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"label_today","type":"text","text":"# TODAY'S OUTPUTS  —  update file nodes each morning after running scripts","x":0,"y":80,"width":2820,"height":70,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"file_relvol","type":"file","file":"05_Data_Pulls/Market/2026-05-01_FMP_RelVol_Screen.md","x":0,"y":160,"width":900,"height":700},
		{"id":"file_orbscreen","type":"file","file":"05_Data_Pulls/Market/2026-05-01_ORB_Entropy_Screen.md","x":960,"y":160,"width":900,"height":700},
		{"id":"file_compression","type":"file","file":"05_Data_Pulls/Market/2026-05-01_Entropy_Compression_Scan.md","x":1920,"y":160,"width":900,"height":700},
		{"id":"label_workflow","type":"text","text":"# DAILY WORKFLOW","x":0,"y":930,"width":900,"height":70,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"text_workflow","type":"text","text":"## 9:00 AM — Pre-Market Screen\n`node run.mjs fmp --rel-vol-screen`\nTop 20 symbols by relative volume\nFilters: price > $5, avg vol ≥ 1M, ATR14 > $0.50, rel vol ≥ 100%\n\n---\n\n## 9:35 AM — ORB Trade Sheet\n`node run.mjs pull orb-entropy`\nBuilds 5-min ORB candle (9:30–9:34 ET)\nApplies: gap + VWAP + range + entropy filters\nCross-references last night's compression scan ★\nVol scalar from SPY 20-day realized vol applied to all sizes\n\n---\n\n## 4:30 PM — Nightly Compression Scan\n`node run.mjs pull entropy-compression-scan`\nScans ~774 symbols: S&P 500 + earnings + thesis watchlist\nFlags symbols with sustained multi-session compression (≤ 0.50)\nFeeds tomorrow morning's ★ column automatically","x":0,"y":1010,"width":900,"height":700},
		{"id":"label_logic","type":"text","text":"# FILTER STACK","x":960,"y":930,"width":900,"height":70,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"text_logic","type":"text","text":"## Quality Filters (applied at 9:35 AM)\n\n| # | Filter | Threshold | Passes When |\n| --- | --- | --- | --- |\n| 1 | Entropy | ≤ 0.60 | `confirmed` status |\n| 2 | Gap alignment | ≥ 0.10% | Gap direction = ORB direction |\n| 3 | VWAP confirmation | — | Entry on correct side of ORB VWAP |\n| 4 | Tight OR range | ≤ 0.50× ATR14 | Coil with room to expand |\n| ★ | Sustained compression | ≤ 0.50 (2+ sessions) | From nightly scan |\n\n---\n\n## Setup Priority\n\n**Prime + ★** = filters 2–4 pass + sustained compression → highest size\n\n**Prime** = filters 2–4 all pass → full size\n\n**Confirmed** = entropy ≤ 0.60 only → standard size\n\n**Active** = direction only, baseline entropy → reduce or skip","x":960,"y":1010,"width":900,"height":700},
		{"id":"label_tiers","type":"text","text":"# SIGNAL QUALITY TIERS","x":1920,"y":930,"width":900,"height":70,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"label_risk","type":"text","text":"# RISK MANAGEMENT","x":0,"y":1780,"width":900,"height":70,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"text_risk","type":"text","text":"## Position Sizing Rules\n\n- **Risk per trade**: 1% of account capital\n- **Max leverage**: 4× account equity (FINRA)\n- **Stop**: 10% × ATR14 — set on fill, never moved\n- **Exit**: 4:00 PM ET market close — no profit target\n- **Re-entry**: one attempt per symbol per session only\n- **Direction flip**: not permitted once entry is triggered\n\n---\n\n## Volatility Targeting (SPY 20-day realised vol)\n\n| Regime | SPY Vol | Size Scalar |\n| --- | --- | --- |\n| Very low | < 10% | 1.50× |\n| Low | 10–15% | up to 1.50× |\n| Normal | 15–25% | 0.60–1.0× |\n| Elevated | 25–35% | 0.43–0.60× |\n| High | > 35% | 0.50× floor |\n\nTarget: 15% annualised — scalar computed and applied automatically each morning","x":0,"y":1860,"width":900,"height":700},
		{"id":"label_thresholds","type":"text","text":"# KEY THRESHOLDS","x":960,"y":1780,"width":900,"height":70,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"text_thresholds","type":"text","text":"## Entropy Buckets\n\n| Bucket | Score | Meaning |\n| --- | --- | --- |\n| Compressed | ≤ 0.25 | Extreme order — rare |\n| Low-entropy-watch | ≤ 0.50 | Strong compression |\n| Near-low-watch | ≤ 0.60 | ORB confirmed |\n| Mixed | ≤ 0.75 | Weak signal |\n| Baseline | > 0.75 | No compression |\n\n---\n\n## ORB Filter Values\n\n| Parameter | Value |\n| --- | --- |\n| ORB window | 9:30–9:34 AM ET |\n| Stop multiplier | 10% × ATR14 |\n| Gap minimum | ≥ 0.10% aligned |\n| OR range / ATR14 | ≤ 0.50× |\n| Entropy lookback | 120 bars (1-min) |\n| Sustained sessions | 2+ consecutive |\n\n---\n\n## Nightly Scan Universe\n\n- S&P 500: 503 constituents\n- Earnings calendar: 200 US-listed (next 7 days)\n- Thesis watchlist: 127 symbols\n- **Total**: ~774 unique symbols","x":960,"y":1860,"width":900,"height":700},
		{"id":"label_docs","type":"text","text":"# REFERENCE DOCS","x":1920,"y":1780,"width":900,"height":70,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"file_playbook","type":"file","file":"04_Reference/ORB + Entropy Strategy Playbook.md","x":1920,"y":1860,"width":900,"height":340},
		{"id":"file_cheatsheet","type":"file","file":"04_Reference/Entropy Strategy Monitoring Cheat Sheet.md","x":1920,"y":2210,"width":900,"height":350},
		{"id":"orb_footer","type":"text","text":"**Scripts**: `scripts/pullers/orb-entropy.mjs` · `scripts/pullers/entropy-compression-scan.mjs`  |  **Scheduler**: `scripts/schedule-orb-tasks.ps1`  |  **Backtest**: `scripts/_backtest_day.mjs`","x":0,"y":2620,"width":2820,"height":60,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"text_tiers","type":"text","text":"## Tier 1 — Prime + Compression ★\nGap ✓  VWAP ✓  Range ✓  Sustained ★\nHighest conviction — maximum size within vol scalar\n\n---\n\n## Tier 2 — Prime\nGap ✓  VWAP ✓  OR/ATR ✓\nAll three quality filters pass, no prior compression\nFull size × vol scalar\n\n---\n\n## Tier 3 — Entropy Confirmed\nEntropy score ≤ 0.60 (near-low-watch or lower)\nStandard size × vol scalar\n\n---\n\n## Tier 4 — Active\nDirection set, entropy baseline (> 0.60)\nReduce size or skip — weakest setup\n\n---\n\n## No Signal\nDOJI open or no intraday data available\nSkip entirely — no trade this symbol today","x":1920,"y":1000,"width":900,"height":700}
	],
	"edges":[]
